       ModelMapper.MapCallback callback)
         throws java.lang.RuntimeException
        For each get/set pair (ignoring blacklisted fields), copy the result of callback to destination. Setters without matching getters on the source are ignored.

        destination - The Model to copy to
        callback - The callback whose return value is set on the destination
